0000"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr><a:t>The true measure of cement is never in the bag, it’s in the structures it creates. Performance becomes visible only when cement transforms into homes, roofs, walls, and foundations that stand strong for generations.</a:t></a:r><a:br><a:rPr lang="en-IN" kern="0" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="FF0000"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr></a:br><a:br><a:rPr lang="en-IN" kern="0" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="FF0000"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr></a:br><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-IN" kern="0" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="FF0000"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr><a:t>In the North East, </a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-IN" kern="0" dirty="0" err="1"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="FF0000"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr><a:t>AmritCem’s</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-IN" kern="0" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="FF0000"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr><a:t> strength is reflected in every resilient building block, every family it protects, and every structure that anchors communities.</a:t></a:r><a:br><a:rPr lang="en-IN" kern="0" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="FF0000"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr></a:br><a:br><a:rPr lang="en-IN" kern="0" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="FF0000"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr></a:br><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-IN" kern="0" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="FF0000"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr><a:t>Showcasing buildings on the cement bag is a direct representation of what the product delivers: reliability, durability, and visible proof of performance. These structures are the living testimonials of </a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-IN" kern="0" dirty="0" err="1"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="FF0000"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr><a:t>AmritCem’s</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-IN" kern="0" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="FF0000"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr><a:t> quality.</a:t></a:r></a:p></p:txBody></p:sp><p:pic><p:nvPicPr><p:cNvPr id="3" name="Picture 2"><a:extLst><a:ext uri="{FF2B5EF4-FFF2-40B4-BE49-F238E27FC236}"><a16:creationId xmlns:a16="http: